_of_Swords-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 57\">Chapter 57</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wineseller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://gameofthrones.wikia.com/wiki/Wineseller\">Wineseller article</a> on the Game of Thrones wikia.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403174211\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.188 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.982 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1909/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11254/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 14599/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3474/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 5344/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.310/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.41 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  942.250      1 -total\n 93.00%  876.270      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 92.81%  874.467      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.57%   99.604     12 Template:Infobox_value\n